import React from 'react'
import './Admin.css'
import Sidebar from '../../components/admin/Sidebar'
import Status from '../../components/admin/Status'
import UserList from '../../components/admin/UserList'
const Admin = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Sidebar/>
      <Status/>
      <UserList/>
    </>
  )
}

export default Admin
